'It is a criminal organisation like the mafia,' said Antonio Mazzitelli, the Mexico and Central America representative to the U.N. Office on Drugs and Crime.

'La Familia, the Knights Templar and, in part, the new, smaller cartels that have developed, like the New Generation Jalisco, are copying this new typology.'

